                            <comment id="13616117" author="dreambird" created="Thu, 28 Mar 2013 07:25:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hey, &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=gates&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;gates&quot;&gt;gates&lt;/a&gt;, I fix this issue by adding detecting logic when substitute the macro arguments.&lt;/p&gt;

