                            <comment id="13721037" author="dreambird" created="Fri, 26 Jul 2013 18:28:23 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;please see discussion in &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-3394&quot; title=&quot;pig parser  complain  same value passed to macro when expanding macro&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PIG-3394&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PIG-3394&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. The original patch detects duplicate arguments, but it should detect duplicate parameters. I will submit new patch to address it.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
